</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="19.[151,1436,152,564]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,403,499,525]" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">Observations:—</emphasis>
This species is differentiated from 
<taxonomicName box="[816,961,500,525]" class="Bacillariophyceae" family="Gomphonemataceae" genus="Gomphoneis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Cymbellales" pageId="19" pageNumber="20" phylum="Ochrophyta" rank="species" species="stoermeri">
<emphasis box="[816,961,500,525]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">G. stoermeri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in being more linear in outline, without the distinct tumid middle section of the valves.
</paragraph>
